title: Benched with Bonnetta: Week 6 Recap (with Kyle Brandt)
itunes:title: Benched with Bonnetta: Week 6 Recap (with Kyle Brandt)
description:
Rachel Bonnetta and company are back for a brand new episode of Benched with Bonnetta! To start, Rachel is joined by Kyle Brandt to recap Week 6 in the NFL and tell you about the surprise guest at her birthday party (2:08). After the break, Rachel and the crew cast the Jimmy Garoppolo biopic (15:52). Finally, Rachel wraps things up by previewing this week's Thursday night game between the Saints and Cardinals (22:41) and tells you the best and worst things she saw over the last week (25:21). 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
